svg.text: It can be see that one area near the top of the head would show a stronger positive signal (darker color) than the rest of the "positive" area of the scalp. Likewise, the blue shading represents the propagation of the signal from the negative pole of the dipole. Electrodes placed on scalp areas over the blue shading would record negative potential.
